  briefing: `<path d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>`,
  
